data.title: Carnarvon, Manawatu
data.meta_description: Carnarvon, Manawatu-Wanganui - New Zealand topographic map. WGS84 coordinates: -40.28853652, 175.36606110.
data.text:
Click a map sheet area on the map to see the download options.

Available NZ Topo50 download formats:

Print ready LINZ maps with legend (TIFF images)

Georeferenced LINZ maps (GeoTIFF images)

Garmin Custom Maps / Google Earth overlays (KMZ files)

Garmin Custom Maps

A list of compatible devices and instructions for copying files to your device is available from Garmin.

MBTiles

Available MBTiles files:

Mainland - 4.3 GB

Chatham Islands - 13.5 MB

Due to the costs associated with providing these large MBTiles files, downloads are available by only. Please consider making a donation to help cover the costs of providing this service.

It is recommended to download and test compatibility with the smaller Chatham Islands file before downloading the large Mainland file.

MBTiles downloads can be used to provide:

Offline mobile maps when used through apps like Locus Map for Android or Guru Maps Pro for iOS.

Topo imagery layers in GIS software like QGIS.

Map imagery when developing your own website maps & apps.

Important Information

The following important information is taken directly from the maps legend:

Representation on this map of a road or track does not necessarily indicate public right of access.

Closed tracks or routes on this map are defined as being no longer maintained or passable and should not be used by recreationalists. The Department of Conservation or other authorities should be contacted for the latest information on tracks and huts.

Not all aerial wires, cableways and obstructions that could be hazardous to aircraft are shown on this map.

Contours and spot elevations in forest and snow areas may be less accurate.
